gencastor (3.2-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Fixed C interfaces generation, only classes and interfaces are
    considered structs for the C world.
  * Fixed name of conversion svc, now is DbCnvSvc everywhere.
  * Fixed calls to commit() and rollback().

 -- Giuseppe Lo Presti <giuseppe.lopresti@cern.ch>  Tue,  3 Ago 2005 18:00:00 +0200

gencastor (3.2-0) unstable; urgency=low

  * Improved SQL code generation, separated scripts for creating and
    dropping the schema.
  * MySQL generation currently disabled.

 -- Giuseppe Lo Presti <giuseppe.lopresti@cern.ch>  Wed, 27 Jul 2005 11:00:00 +0200

